Package com.ecom.enums

package com.ecom.enums
Provides Enums to represent constant choices.

This package contains custom Enums to avoid typo issues and leverages constant choices

Example usages include:

invalid input: '<'>ul
  • Represents the authors of the test cases using EAuthors
  • Represents the name of the browsers using EBrowsers
  • Represents the name of the Categories using ECategories
  • Represents the key presents in the config file using Econfig
  • Represents the name of the Devices using EDevices
  • Represents the names of the system information using EsystemInfo
  • Represents the names of the wait strategy using EwaitStrategy
